As Blackstorm stood in the spot indicated. Maxima turned to the console, 
touched a button.

A light came from above as it showered Blackstorm with it's erie light. 

"No, Blackstorm. You need not bother yourself with anything." her optics 
watched Blackstorm for a moment. 

Then her crimson optics turned to the console screen as it showed a complete 
skematics of her. "I won't worry about what Hydras has in mind." as she typed 
in a few things quickly on the console. 

The light disappeared. "That is all, Blackstorm. Thank you." As she still 
worked at the console not facing Blackstorm at all. 

--part1_15.14a4143c.2c32304b_boundary
